I mean, a 13-year-old
guitar prodigy,

00:06.423 --> 00:07.925
and she's a chick;
that's cool, man.

00:07.925 --> 00:09.218
I know. I know.

00:09.218 --> 00:11.720
She--she's a massive
Gaga fan.

00:11.720 --> 00:14.014
She saw me in that Gibson ad.
She made the connection.

00:14.014 --> 00:16.058
And it's, like,
a Make-a-Wish-type thing, right?

00:16.058 --> 00:18.143
Yeah, Dream-a-Music-Dream
Foundation.

00:18.143 --> 00:19.728
"Meet your hero."
She picked me.

00:19.728 --> 00:21.605
And does she have,
like, cancer or something?

00:21.605 --> 00:23.148
No, lupus.

00:23.148 --> 00:24.983
Oh, oh, oh, okay.
Well, that explains it.

00:24.983 --> 00:26.318
Explains what?

00:26.318 --> 00:27.819
Well, I mean,
if she was a cancer kid,

00:27.819 --> 00:29.488
she would meet actual
famous people, like--

00:29.488 --> 00:31.740
I don't know--
Jeter and, you know, Gaga.

00:31.740 --> 00:33.033
You know what I mean?
The A-list.

00:33.033 --> 00:34.535
But you're not on the A-list.

00:34.535 --> 00:36.161
You're on the lupus list,
which is fine.

00:36.161 --> 00:38.413
She can't go out in the sun,
she can't have candy

00:38.413 --> 00:41.250
or ice cream, so yeah,
she's basically a shut-in.

00:41.250 --> 00:43.085
And I--
dude, I know, that sucks,

00:43.085 --> 00:45.712
but see, if she was, like,
a cancer kid, she'd meet Adele.

00:45.712 --> 00:47.756
I bet you Adele's, like,
the number one attraction

00:47.756 --> 00:49.675
for cancer kids right now.

00:49.675 --> 00:52.928
It's amazing, because only you
could turn this into a negative.

00:52.928 --> 00:54.429
(scoffs)

00:54.429 --> 00:56.098
You know who could turn it
into a positive?

00:56.098 --> 00:57.766
-Who?
-Adele.

00:57.766 --> 00:59.309
(...) you.

00:59.309 --> 01:01.144
I'm just thinking
about Tenika, pal.

01:01.144 --> 01:02.688
No, you're just jealous.

01:02.688 --> 01:03.855
I'm jealous?

01:03.855 --> 01:06.024
-Yeah.
-What am I jealous of?

01:06.024 --> 01:08.068
Because you're not
on the goddamn lupus list...

01:08.068 --> 01:09.653
-Oh.
-'Cause I am, asshole.

01:09.653 --> 01:11.029
Oh, okay. All right.
Yeah, yeah.

01:11.029 --> 01:12.406
(women screaming)

01:12.406 --> 01:13.657
What the hell
is that about?

01:13.657 --> 01:15.784
What?

01:15.784 --> 01:17.452
