from "The New York Times."

01:17.452 --> 01:18.912
-Oh, my God!
-Oh, my God.

01:18.912 --> 01:20.163
-Awesome.
-I know.

01:20.163 --> 01:21.081
Holy shit, honey.

01:21.081 --> 01:22.541
