01:28.255 --> 01:30.007
and, oh, what a star she is."

01:30.007 --> 01:31.425
Oh, my God, honey.

01:31.425 --> 01:32.884
That's awesome.

01:32.884 --> 01:34.553
"Imagine Sharon Stone
if she could sing.

01:34.553 --> 01:36.430
