vixen whisky in her voice."

01:38.432 --> 01:40.225
Oh, my God.

01:40.225 --> 01:42.686
"With outstanding support from
the members of The Assassins

01:42.686 --> 01:45.314
"and the feathery touch
of piano player AJ Jenkins,

01:45.314 --> 01:47.107
