tour guitarist Flash..."

01:49.318 --> 01:51.528
Oh, my God!
That's so awesome. Hey, pal.

01:51.528 --> 01:54.448
"Ava X is the new name
for an accomplished artist

01:54.448 --> 01:56.491
just hitting
her very promised success."

01:56.491 --> 01:58.201
-Yes!
-Look at the picture of her.

01:58.201 --> 01:59.244
I know. I know. I know.

01:59.244 --> 02:02.998
You look fantastic, honey.
Wow.

02:02.998 --> 02:05.751
And did they--
did they mention The Heathens?

02:05.751 --> 02:07.794
'Cause, no, I mean,
he mentioned the backup singers,

02:07.794 --> 02:08.920
