what I'm talking about.

02:30.108 --> 02:31.401
-Phew.
-I love it.

02:31.401 --> 02:32.569
-Yeah, yeah, yeah.
-It's--

02:32.569 --> 02:34.821
-Yeah.
-Look at this one.

02:34.821 --> 02:36.114
Yes!

02:36.114 --> 02:38.742
Hey, so how do you--
how do you think

02:38.742 --> 02:39.868
