process is gonna be, 'cause--

02:51.338 --> 02:53.715
So, yes, because it's got
kind of, like, a nice flow...

02:53.715 --> 02:55.967
You know, Flash and I are
already writing all these songs

02:55.967 --> 02:58.762
for Gigi, and now we're gonna
have to write more Ava X songs,

02:58.762 --> 03:00.972
