you know, maybe

03:00.972 --> 03:03.642
we just slow the process down
a little bit, you know?

03:03.642 --> 03:05.435
-Johnny? Johnny.
-What?

03:05.435 --> 03:06.812
We got it covered.

03:06.812 --> 03:08.230
Oh. Okay.

03:08.230 --> 03:09.815
-Yeah, see, I love that.
-Oh. Come here.

03:09.815 --> 03:11.650
-Come here, look at this one.
-I love it.

03:11.650 --> 03:13.985
Hey, dude, we've been messing
around with some song ideas.

03:13.985 --> 03:16.238
We're actually gonna make a demo
at my place later, so...

03:16.238 --> 03:17.989
-Oh.
-We got it covered.

03:17.989 --> 03:19.491
Look at this.

03:19.491 --> 03:21.076
I love that you've thought
about this.

03:21.076 --> 03:22.369
Good.
Well, that's, you know--

03:22.369 --> 03:23.745
-That's good.
-Makes it easier.

03:23.745 --> 03:24.746
Put one here.
Bang.

03:24.746 --> 03:26.164
