will do that?

03:29.626 --> 03:31.211
I can do that
in, like, ten minutes.

03:31.211 --> 03:32.963
What color clothes
you want to wear?

03:32.963 --> 03:34.256
I think I'm gonna maybe
go with something...

03:34.256 --> 03:38.510
What?
No! Not a chance.

03:38.510 --> 03:40.637
He wants to have my children.

03:40.637 --> 03:41.972
Right.

03:41.972 --> 03:44.683
