going to look like

04:49.956 --> 04:52.000
by opening night--
Campbell's idea.

04:52.000 --> 04:56.505
He says, "See it. Believe it.
And then become it."

04:56.505 --> 04:57.756
Very, very Method.

04:57.756 --> 04:59.090
All right, you know what,
dude?

04:59.090 --> 05:00.926
He's not De Niro

05:00.926 --> 05:02.636
in his "Raging Bull" days, okay?

05:02.636 --> 05:04.262
And he is nowhere near
Daniel Day-Lewis.

05:04.262 --> 05:05.722
That guy stays in character

05:05.722 --> 05:07.891
the entire time
he's shooting a picture.

05:07.891 --> 05:10.977
Campbell is gonna have
the whole cast and crew fast

05:10.977 --> 05:13.939
for three weeks
before opening night

05:13.939 --> 05:16.024
so we can feel the famine

05:16.024 --> 05:17.526
in our bones.

05:17.526 --> 05:19.194
That's 100 people.

05:19.194 --> 05:21.613
That's like having an army
of Daniel Day-De Niros.

05:21.613 --> 05:22.989
Who can barely stand up!

05:24.115 --> 05:25.325
Okay.

05:25.325 --> 05:27.369
Just come back to the fold, man.

05:27.369 --> 05:30.038
Campbell directed and starred in

05:30.038 --> 05:33.667
a highly acclaimed movie
of "Hamlet" a few years back.

05:33.667 --> 05:37.921
Yesterday at rehearsal, I heard
he wants to do the same thing

05:37.921 --> 05:39.297
with "Feast," man.

05:39.297 --> 05:41.132
So forget the Obies.

05:41.132 --> 05:43.343
Forget the Tonys.

05:43.343 --> 05:44.719
Me and you,

05:44.719 --> 05:47.305
we could be going
to the Oscars, bro.

05:47.305 --> 05:49.391
The friggin' Oscars.

05:50.934 --> 05:52.936
I--
I want back in, bro.

05:52.936 --> 05:54.563
-Yes!
-You'll talk to him for me?

05:54.563 --> 05:59.192
You bet your ball sack,
I will, buddy.

05:59.192 --> 06:01.027
But you have to fast
like the rest of us.

06:01.027 --> 06:03.446
I'm Jewish.
Fasting's in my blood.

06:03.446 --> 06:05.198
Okay.

06:05.198 --> 06:07.450
You have to promise to only
shoot me from skinny angles.

06:13.748 --> 06:16.710
