06:28.763 --> 06:31.725
-Wow!
-Whoo!

06:31.725 --> 06:33.643
Oh, my God, that was awesome.

06:33.643 --> 06:34.811
You were awesome.

06:34.811 --> 06:36.062
Man, you can play that ax.

06:36.062 --> 06:37.397
Thank you.

06:37.397 --> 06:40.692
Hey, can we write
an actual song?

06:40.692 --> 06:42.152
Oh, honey, I'd love to,

06:42.152 --> 06:43.695
but I only had a couple hours
to do this,

06:43.695 --> 06:45.071
'cause I got
a songwriting session with Ava.

06:45.071 --> 06:46.406
No, it's--
it's fine.

06:46.406 --> 06:48.158
This was so cool.

06:48.158 --> 06:49.242
Hey, you know what?

06:49.242 --> 06:50.827
We could write a song together.

06:50.827 --> 06:52.912
You could be my new
songwriting partner if you want.

06:52.912 --> 06:54.456
-Really?
-Yeah.

06:54.456 --> 06:56.499
Is that okay if we jam
for a couple hours?

06:56.499 --> 06:59.419
