07:18.355 --> 07:19.356
All right.

07:19.356 --> 07:20.815
Thank you so much.

07:20.815 --> 07:22.275
-Yeah, no problem.
-You're amazing.

07:22.275 --> 07:23.735
Give me a hug.

07:23.735 --> 07:24.653
Good job.

07:26.488 --> 07:28.156
Hey.

07:28.156 --> 07:29.532
What's, uh--
what are we doing?

07:29.532 --> 07:30.533
"What are we doing?"

07:30.533 --> 07:31.826
Yeah, what's--

07:31.826 --> 07:33.495
what's going on
with us right now?

07:33.495 --> 07:36.206
